OL,3,CChurch leaders threaten legal action
OL,4,Cover dangerous collapsed wall
OL,6,FLeaders of a church in Shropshire are
OL,7,Fpreparing to take legal action against
OL,8,Fthe town council amid claims delays to
OL,9,Frepair the Ludlow Town Walls could be
OL,10,Fputting the historic church at risk,
OL,11,FLewis Warner reports.
OL,13,FCampaigners say inaction by Ludlow
OL,14,FTown Council over rebuilding a section
OL,15,Fof the walls which collapsed 12 years
OL,16,Fago is now risking the stability of St
OL,17,FLaurence's Church.
