OL,3,CChurch leaders threaten legal action
OL,4,Cover dangerous collapsed wall
OL,6,FThe church have threatened to take
OL,7,Flegal action against the council if it
OL,8,Fdoes not start to work together to get
OL,9,Fthe wall repaired.
OL,11,FRobert Owen from St Laurence's Church
OL,12,Fsaid: "To this day the town council
OL,13,Fwho are responsible for the
OL,14,Fmaintenance of this wall have made no
OL,15,Fprogress in getting the repairs done.
OL,17,F"The church has now run out of
OL,18,Fpatience with this situation, we are
OL,19,Fseriously concerned about the effects
OL,20,Fof the collapsed wall on the stability
OL,21,Fof the church itself."
