OL,10,FHowever, it still has not made public
OL,11,Fa crucial a crucial structural report
OL,12,Fon the wall.
OL,14,FDarren Childs, from Ludlow Residents
OL,15,FGroup, said: "It's unbelievable that
OL,16,Fit hasn't been released over the last
OL,17,F12 years.
