OL,6,F"The report was completed in 2021 and
OL,7,Fsince then the council have held it
OL,8,Fand refused to share it with anyone
OL,9,Felse."
OL,11,FLudlow Town Council has been contacted
OL,12,Ffor comment but has not yet responded.
OL,13,FIt has previously said that the Town
OL,14,FWalls Trust should be the body to look
OL,15,Finto cost-effective repair solutions.
OL,17,FColin Richards, Ludlow Town Walls
OL,18,FTrust, said: "I think with legal
OL,19,Faction, it costs a lot of money and in
OL,20,Fsome respects it's a negative process.
